com.hazelcast.cache.impl

Class HazelcastCacheManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.cache.impl.HazelcastCacheManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, javax.cache.CacheManager
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HazelcastClientCacheManager, HazelcastServerCacheManager

    public abstract class HazelcastCacheManager
extends Object
implements javax.cache.CacheManager
    The Hazelcast CacheManager base class. Hazelcast supports two modes:
    • Client - HazelcastClientCacheManager
    • Server - HazelcastServerCacheManager
    See Also:
    CacheManager
